      <head xml:id="DRMorrisonetal_DurnessGMacKenzieagriculture-d0e37">1. Land division and allocation</head>
      <head xml:id="DRMorrisonetal_DurnessGMacKenzieagriculture-d0e43" subtype="h2">(a) Specific portions or allotments into which arable land is divided</head>
