      <head xml:id="DRMorrisonetal_DurnessGMacKenzieagriculture-d0e151">2. Harness of a horse</head>
      <head xml:id="DRMorrisonetal_DurnessGMacKenzieagriculture-d0e157" subtype="h2">(a) The harness of a horse as used in the performance of different tasks</head>
